                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-1 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Māryām qǝddǝst dǝngǝl ʾǝmmu la-ʾIyasus Krǝstos kahāli ...
                        "O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of Jesus Christ the Almighty ..."
                           (<locus target="#6rb">6rb</locus>) (cp. ChRep n<locus target="#373">373</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- salām laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Māryām ʾǝmma bǝrhān wa-ʾǝmma madḫǝn ...
                        "Salutation to you, o my Lady Mary, Mother of the Light and Mother of the
                        Saviour ..." (<locus from="6rb" to="7ra">6rb-7ra</locus>).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The miracles of St Mary (Text I-5) and of Jesus (Text II) are
                        numbered.</note>
                  </msItem>
